# Fraud Detection Project

## Overview
This project analyzes and models credit card transactions to detect fraudulent activities.  
It explores data distributions, relationships between transaction features, and implements visualization techniques to understand fraud patterns.

The project includes:
- Data exploration and visualization
- Feature analysis
- Fraud vs non-fraud comparisons
- Preliminary insights for predictive modeling

---

## Dataset

The dataset used in this project is the [Fraud Detection Using ML Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/prasannakrish12/fraud-detection-using-ml-dataset/data).  

